 from jeff mri com jonathan jefferies subject bmw four nine r rally summary memorial day weekend rally keywords bmw rally four nine r article i d mri one nine nine three apr nine zero one one seven four three one nine zero three expires tue one jun one nine nine three zero seven zero zero zero zero gmt distribution rec motorcycles organization microtec research santa clara california usa lines six six bbbbbbbb mm mm ww ww bb bb mm m m mm ww ww b b mm m m mm ww w ww bbbbbbbb mm m m mm ww w w ww bb bb mm m mm ww w w ww bb bb mm mm ww w w ww bbbbbbbb mm mm ww ww press release to all bmw riders subject rally time is here from bmw club of northern california bmw four nine er rally may two seven three one u s memorial day weekend san francisco bay area two zero th annual bmw four nine er rally sponsored by the bmw club of northern califronia will be held at the quincy california fairgrounds from may two seven three one one nine nine three included in the four two pre registration fee four seven at gate are four star camping field events and trophies two dinners rally pin door prizes poker run vendor displays fun run english trials and live music playing throughout the weekend plus extras like hot showers tours a concourse d elegance and more this is first time in the four nine er rally s two zero year history that the event is being held in quincy and according to pat gardner rally chairman the four nine er rally s continuing growth and the need for a larger and more complete facility led us to quincy plus we can get there on either of our two most favrite highways highway seven zero which goes through the feather river canyon or up from the south via the northernmost part of the gold country s highway four nine day passes will not be available and non bmw rider must be a pre registered guest of a bmw rider the quincy fairgrounds is located on california state highway seven zero eight nine two miles south of downtown quincy for pre registration forms and additional information write doug hubbard bmw club of northern california four one two three six norman court fremont ca nine four five three nine or telephone five one zero six five one two one nine five additional notes this is a not for profit event and riders do get their monies worth whether you ve ever attended a rally before or not this is the one to make the only problem has been that there are so many activities that attendees have to choose one over another quincy is a beautiful campground lots of grass and little dust for folks who have been to previous four nine er rallies at mariposa quincy has lots of space all of it flat so room is not a problem there are buildings and such available if there is a change in the weather also the people of quincy are going all out to welcome us registration will begin on thursday of course there are always early arrivals who will show up monday or tuesday the registration fee pays for camping thursday through monday five days there will be a tour friday with the main events beginning saturday sunday evening will be the awards ceremony for members of the various clubs club awards will be based on registration declaration of affilitation there will of course be the usual awards for oldest male and female rider and youngest rider they get cheater permits at one five and greatest distance one up two up and all the usual things